Class CollectionOfBooks

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • model.CollectionOfBooks

  • public class CollectionOfBooks
extends java.util.Observable
    A CollectionOfBooks contains a ArrayList of Book objects. The list can be manipulated by adding and removing Book objects.
